Thanks guys, thanks Jon, my friend...as you all can see, as always interest is pretty low, lowest of all today's shows: 37 full downloads and 16 people stayed as seeders (statistics for first 6h). It is, unfortunately too low to push Burn Notice in my schedule.
However, I will follow through the whole season and no further requests or "reminders" are needed.

@greyscales: LOL, after I read few very, very negative articles about Deep End I wasn't even tempted. Especially when I found out that Billy Zane is one of the cast members. I was sure then, like gazillion percent.

@benjohn: It is simply too big for me. I am just one guy with two years old PC and very limited connection speed.

@steve: Vampire Diaries - I cannot tell you how many times I was asked the same and explained my reasons for: No, thanks.
